    "body" : "<p>This is fixed in <a href=\"https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/javase/15-relnote-issues.html#JDK-8244245\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">JDK 15</a>. Use <code>localizedBy()</code> (and <em>not</em> <code>localizedWith()</code>):</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>formatter\n    .localizedBy(myLocale)\n    .format(...)\n</code></pre>\n<p>For Java versions prior to 15, format like this:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>formatter\n    .localizedBy(myLcoale)\n    .withDecimalStyle(DecimalStyle.of(myLocale))\n    .format(...)\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
